Branch: Similarity Testing & Async Processing

This branch focuses on improving the accuracy, performance, and scalability of the plagiarism detection system. 
The primary goal is to refine similarity computation while preparing the system for efficient large-scale processing.

Focus Areas

Similarity threshold testing and optimization
Tokenization, k-gram, and fingerprint refinement
Non-blocking similarity computation with background jobs

Goals

Improve detection accuracy
Reduce false positives
Enhance scalability and responsiveness
